CONVENIENCE IS KEY AND THIS HOUSE IS ALSO NERABY TO A HOSPITAL, SCHOOLS, RESTAURANTS, WALMART, AND SO MUCH MORE. HOA INCLUDES INTERNET AND CABLE.
